Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.82,0:00:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.71,0:00:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备好了就叫我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.42,0:00:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也来帮忙啊
